column1: Weighted MRI visualization size (256, 128, 1) in T2 of the skull of a man of 37 years old, with axial section n°71 starting at the base of the skull. The section reveals the presence of: the left cerebellar cortex of volume 1166.7480 mm³, the fourth ventricle of volume 2.6367 mm³, the brainstem of volume 217.5293 mm³ and the right cerebellar cortex of volume 1223.4375 mm³.
